Package edu.ncsu.csc316.trail.manager

Class TrailManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc316.trail.manager.TrailManager
  • public class TrailManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the data of the files passed. TrailManager finds the distances to destinations given an origin. It can fetch Landmarks by LandmarkID. It can get a List of proposed first aid stations based on the minimum number of intersecting trails.
    Author:
    Ben Morris
